AMD<a href="http://www.marketwatch.com/story/amd-joins-meego-linux-open-source-project-for-next-generation-mobile-embedded-platforms-2010-11-15">宣布</a> <a href="http://lwn.net/Articles/415467/">加入Linux基金会的MeeGo项目</a>。<i>
